Package: StatsTFLValR
Type: Package
Title: Audit-Ready Clinical Validation Utilities for SDTM, ADaM, and TFL Workflows
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mangesh", "Kalsekar", 
           email = "kalsekar.mangesh@gmail.com", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides utilities for clinical trial data validation and statistical
             programming across CDISC SDTM, ADaM, and TFL workflows. Functions support
             dataset loading, SUPP merging, derivations, population and Big-N
             computations, frequency and summary table construction, and
             PROC COMPARE-style dataset comparison reports. The package emphasizes
             reproducibility, traceability, and audit-ready outputs suitable for
             regulated clinical research environments.
